<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>This is a demonstration application for testing .NET compatibility across different architectures (x86 and ARM).</p>

<h3>Data Collection</h3>
<p>This application collects the following system information for compatibility testing purposes:</p>
<ul>
    <li>System architecture (x86, x64, ARM64)</li>
    <li>Operating system information</li>
    <li>.NET runtime version</li>
    <li>Machine name and user name</li>
    <li>Memory usage statistics</li>
    <li>Performance benchmark results</li>
</ul>

<h3>Data Storage</h3>
<p>All data is stored locally in a SQLite database and is not transmitted to external servers.</p>

<h3>Purpose</h3>
<p>The collected data is used solely for:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Demonstrating system compatibility</li>
    <li>Performance comparison between architectures</li>
    <li>Testing application functionality across platforms</li>
</ul>

<h3>Contact</h3>
<p>This is a demonstration application. For questions about .NET compatibility testing, please refer to the official Microsoft documentation.</p>
